title: Cyber Warfare - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 3/25/22

description:
Guest host Richard Syrett and author Sean Patrick Hazlett explore how technology will change the future of warfare, how misinformation is aiding Ukraine in its war with Russia, and if World War Three may have actually already begun.
